{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~ejw/authoring/redmond/access_control/tsld014.htm", "content": "\r\n<HTML>\r\n\r\n<HEAD>\r\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html;charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Microsoft Internet Assistant for PowerPoint 97\">\r\n <TITLE>Security: Encryption</TITLE> \r\n</HEAD>\r\n\r\n<BODY     >\r\n\r\n <H1>Security: Encryption</H1> \r\n <P><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Encryption could greatly reduce chance of snooping\r\n</H2>\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Snooping is particularly dangerous when account names are sent across the wire\r\n</H2>\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Recommend but not require that implementations support encryption\r\n</H2>\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Allow implementations to refuse non-encrypted requests</H2>\r\n</UL></P>\r\n<P></P> \r\n<P>\r\n<TABLE>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=100> <A HREF=\"tsld013.htm\">Previous slide</A> </TD>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=100> <A HREF=\"tsld015.htm\">Next slide</A> </TD>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=150> <A HREF=\"tsld001.htm\">Back to first slide</A> </TD>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=150> <A HREF=\"sld014.htm\">View graphic version</A> </TD>\r\n</TABLE>\r\n<BR>\r\n</P>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</Body>\r\n</HTML>\r\n", "encoding": "ascii"}